lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>S</span><sup>2</sup><sub><span
lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>d</span></sub>)</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>L<sub>vc</sub></span>
– индуктивность ЗК<i><span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%'>(</span></i><i><span
lang=DE style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-ansi-language:DE'>vc</span></i><i><span
