mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><span
style='mso-tab-count:1'>                </span>n = (BL / S<sub>d</sub>)<sup>2</sup></span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i
 style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'><sup><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
