</v:shape></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>(p<sub>0 </sub>/ (2&#960;cR<sub>e</sub>M<sub>as</sub><sup>2</sup>))</span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i
 style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Cambria Math","serif";
