 <v:imagedata src="Перевод%20Шорта.files/image022.png" o:title="" chromakey="white"/>
</v:shape></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:
